[
  {
    "text": "So, when I was little, I made a mess of my room like any other child, my age.",
    "uid": "caa7976bc0b9b47d",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 8.59,
    "end": 17.35
  },
  {
    "text": "The difference between me and other kids, the person overseeing my cleanup, was my stepfather Rick.",
    "uid": "cdf2f8426ed78ed9",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 17.35,
    "end": 28.03
  },
  {
    "text": "And Rick was an attorney and in the military.",
    "uid": "49c1c55fdf64cbb7",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 28.11,
    "end": 33.03
  },
  {
    "text": "He was very stoic, removed, emotionless.",
    "uid": "9c109b79e6d34bba",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 33.75,
    "end": 38.59
  },
  {
    "text": "And I used to joke and say that he was kind of like C3PO, but with less emotion.",
    "uid": "f397b4b1c5b199ba",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 39.47,
    "end": 48.83
  },
  {
    "text": "And then it turned on me recently that joke actually doesn't make any sense.",
    "uid": "5988d67ef76984d5",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 52.3,
    "end": 57.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Because C3PO is very emotional.",
    "uid": "7365a19422d7a047",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 57.78,
    "end": 61.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Just like, ah, too, where are you?",
    "uid": "e58cc0f69a3f08a5",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 61.78,
    "end": 66.32
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, like my stepfather was never in a panic looking for me.",
    "uid": "10a77a3a605bd96b",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 66.32,
    "end": 71.32
  },
  {
    "text": "The way C3PO was looking for R2.",
    "uid": "1e06a1ef6b183829",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 72.32,
    "end": 75.32
  },
  {
    "text": "So, cleaning up my room, I was given an allotted time.",
    "uid": "98fd5546e65a2161",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 76.32,
    "end": 83.92
  },
  {
    "text": "And Rick would come in and whatever was out of place.",
    "uid": "9a8a4ab3dce708fd",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 84.92,
    "end": 88.92
  },
  {
    "text": "He would put in a large trash bag and then he'd lock it in the trunk of the car.",
    "uid": "07947fe99f7904fa",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 88.92,
    "end": 94.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Then I had to do chores to earn money to buy my toys back.",
    "uid": "98ba6d83dd19f2a7",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 95.92,
    "end": 101.92
  },
  {
    "text": "And it sounds harsh because it is.",
    "uid": "7c20b23021f70023",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 101.92,
    "end": 110.95
  },
  {
    "text": "But to be fair, they were, they were price fairly.",
    "uid": "663becab49226734",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 117.3,
    "end": 123.3
  },
  {
    "text": "I could buy entire millennium falcons, wind up evil canables, and stuff monkeys for like a nickel each.",
    "uid": "f2ab0cb09c752acd",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 127.74,
    "end": 137.74
  },
  {
    "text": "But Rick, what he was, he was hardcore.",
    "uid": "d735db779a6d0e47",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 141.74,
    "end": 143.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Like holidays we weren't even allowed to have friends or family over the house.",
    "uid": "75cea2762121ff55",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 144.74,
    "end": 149.74
  },
  {
    "text": "He claimed our house was not big enough.",
    "uid": "d99cf447e4138b41",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 150.74,
    "end": 152.74
  },
  {
    "text": "So that was not true.",
    "uid": "79e657a43be9b7a8",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 153.74,
    "end": 155.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Meanwhile, my mother was very emotional and passionate and affectionate.",
    "uid": "ec0313b4543c62a1",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 158.02,
    "end": 164.02
  },
  {
    "text": "She was wild and funny.",
    "uid": "9878be61fec637fb",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 165.02,
    "end": 167.02
  },
  {
    "text": "She's originally from Southern Mississippi and was raised in a very conservative house.",
    "uid": "f8d3f698add447a1",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 168.02,
    "end": 174.02
  },
  {
    "text": "And she was always just wanting to make sure that I knew the most important thing in life was to be happy.",
    "uid": "bd33458b57ad1759",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 175.02,
    "end": 185.02
  },
  {
    "text": "And she just supported anything.",
    "uid": "068ca3f0599acb22",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 186.02,
    "end": 189.02
  },
  {
    "text": "I did anything I did was so cool and I always looked adorable and just everything was great.",
    "uid": "25d168dc01075df2",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 190.02,
    "end": 194.02
  },
  {
    "text": "And like even down to dropping out of high school.",
    "uid": "89d86c4a995db792",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 195.02,
    "end": 197.02
  },
  {
    "text": "My mother would brag to people.",
    "uid": "d90279657d9a7bc4",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 199.02,
    "end": 201.02
  },
  {
    "text": "She was like, yeah, I take drop down, you know, she's doing her own thing.",
    "uid": "360716ccea51c69f",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 202.02,
    "end": 206.02
  },
  {
    "text": "And my own thing.",
    "uid": "2d7044447f4571bc",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 209.74,
    "end": 211.74
  },
  {
    "text": "I had nothing going on.",
    "uid": "10d4fa5ea26f13b3",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 212.74,
    "end": 213.74
  },
  {
    "text": "I was like, we're going to repeat the parlor or sound pobleways.",
    "uid": "3694b648586b22ef",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 214.74,
    "end": 218.74
  },
  {
    "text": "That was me doing something.",
    "uid": "db0fff75434ae760",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 219.74,
    "end": 221.74
  },
  {
    "text": "And then I found stand up comedy.",
    "uid": "56706336b435b5ff",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 222.74,
    "end": 226.74
  },
  {
    "text": "And I immediately had focused in my life.",
    "uid": "513309bd205f902d",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 227.74,
    "end": 230.74
  },
  {
    "text": "And I was so passionate and excited about it.",
    "uid": "e1f552397e726729",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 230.74,
    "end": 233.74
  },
  {
    "text": "And my mother, you know, she didn't care if I was in some dingy club in middle America or on TV.",
    "uid": "3404e93e8df7456b",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 234.74,
    "end": 240.74
  },
  {
    "text": "She just thought I was cool. You know, as long as I was happy, she was happy.",
    "uid": "82e9deac9003ba83",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 241.74,
    "end": 244.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell me that my career was a waste of my time and a waste of my intelligence.",
    "uid": "482fa1b177dc985c",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 251.24,
    "end": 259.83
  },
  {
    "text": "And he thought that I should be a doctor or a lawyer.",
    "uid": "da013e0a7aeb0953",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 259.83,
    "end": 263.83
  },
  {
    "text": "He suggested that I quit comedy and go to business school.",
    "uid": "545fe274ee62e63e",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 264.83,
    "end": 268.83
  },
  {
    "text": "Like, even just a couple of years ago.",
    "uid": "04843e0a8aa23341",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 269.83,
    "end": 272.83
  },
  {
    "text": "When my career was going fine, I was making good money.",
    "uid": "1178eb3149b50b68",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 273.83,
    "end": 277.83
  },
  {
    "text": "I said, so you're telling me if I quit comedy and went to business school.",
    "uid": "7a0e0336c73159e1",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 278.83,
    "end": 282.83
  },
  {
    "text": "Something I'm not at all interested in.",
    "uid": "ada47d824edd7d10",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 283.83,
    "end": 286.83
  },
  {
    "text": "And then it up working in like a cubicle in a office somewhere with the life sucked out of me.",
    "uid": "27808693ddc23d65",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 286.83,
    "end": 293.83
  },
  {
    "text": "You would support that. And he said, absolutely.",
    "uid": "54ee3ab765fd74b3",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 294.83,
    "end": 300.3
  },
  {
    "text": "So, um, although my mother was very supportive of me, we certainly had our differences and problems.",
    "uid": "7f4bfaca6edc60ad",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 310.95,
    "end": 319.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And I remember one time like a decade ago being on the phone fighting.",
    "uid": "f7d723d5abd82a67",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 319.95,
    "end": 326.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And when the argument went going anywhere, when I was mid-sentence, she just abruptly handed the phone to Rick.",
    "uid": "fd78b776b7c67488",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 327.95,
    "end": 335.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And he said, TIG, your mother doesn't want to talk to you.",
    "uid": "a35dcc4e24c39d29",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 336.95,
    "end": 340.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And he just hung up on me.",
    "uid": "08ab385f3aad3505",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 341.95,
    "end": 342.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And I kept calling back, no answer. It was so frustrating and stifling.",
    "uid": "ebd0d4d8025c0341",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 343.95,
    "end": 347.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And, um, this march, my phone rang and the word parents popped up on my caller ID.",
    "uid": "0a2d13982a054d40",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 347.95,
    "end": 358.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And I was like, oh, this is probably my mother calling to wish me a happy birthday.",
    "uid": "73bf265f442a8151",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 359.95,
    "end": 363.95
  },
  {
    "text": "Because a couple of days before it was my birthday and I had Mr. Call.",
    "uid": "74f4b88a1c784233",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 364.95,
    "end": 367.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And when I answered the phone, it was Rick.",
    "uid": "fc394c3ed51fda01",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 368.95,
    "end": 370.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And Rick has only called me like two times in my entire life.",
    "uid": "be4b748925d05aa2",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 371.95,
    "end": 374.95
  },
  {
    "text": "One was to tell me, I have no idea what that was about.",
    "uid": "621585884dfc5fa7",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 374.95,
    "end": 379.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And the second time was this time. And he was calling to tell me that my mother had fallen",
    "uid": "e74e7c2e085a60e8",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 380.95,
    "end": 385.95
  },
  {
    "text": "and hit her head and was not going to make it.",
    "uid": "6834961649db23fd",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 386.95,
    "end": 389.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And I immediately pictured her lying in a hospital just barely hanging on saying, you know,",
    "uid": "87852a9a5dfd450a",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 391.95,
    "end": 402.95
  },
  {
    "text": "call TIG, tell her to come to Texas to say goodbye.",
    "uid": "4b857244f8dc574e",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 402.95,
    "end": 408.95
  },
  {
    "text": "And I said, can I talk to my mother?",
    "uid": "b707dc7240f3252a",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 411.42,
    "end": 414.42
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, put her on the phone and he said, no, you can't ever talk to her again.",
    "uid": "956c1146916eb36e",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 415.42,
    "end": 420.42
  },
  {
    "text": "My mother had suffered massive brain hemorrhaging with zero chance of recovery.",
    "uid": "67250f95d2ead850",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 421.42,
    "end": 428.42
  },
  {
    "text": "And it was really so intense to process that that I would never be able to talk to her again.",
    "uid": "5bbce7e7c05bd2a1",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 428.42,
    "end": 441.7
  },
  {
    "text": "I've reflected a lot recently about that phone call over a decade ago when we were arguing.",
    "uid": "85db6adeec37254a",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 444.37,
    "end": 452.37
  },
  {
    "text": "And I thought about how I know my mother would give anything in the world to be able to come back to talk to me.",
    "uid": "2574feee92f649a8",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 452.37,
    "end": 465.37
  },
  {
    "text": "And I always think that if somebody could be like, okay, you can come back,",
    "uid": "4f81ac177b2f76ce",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 466.37,
    "end": 471.37
  },
  {
    "text": "but you have to come back to that phone call where you're fighting with TIG.",
    "uid": "1547f11d5c5c02c1",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 472.37,
    "end": 477.37
  },
  {
    "text": "There would be zero fighting.",
    "uid": "457f9a32ec747b6e",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 477.37,
    "end": 481.37
  },
  {
    "text": "It would be only, I love yous and I'm sorry, from both of us.",
    "uid": "b69a911974e94574",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 482.37,
    "end": 497.18
  },
  {
    "text": "After my mother's funeral, we left Mississippi our hometown where she was buried and we're driving back to Texas.",
    "uid": "865bbb8bd822d7e3",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 498.18,
    "end": 508.18
  },
  {
    "text": "And my brother and my uncle were in one car and we're in the other.",
    "uid": "13d20da268a158d6",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 508.18,
    "end": 515.91
  },
  {
    "text": "And we were driving and he said, too, I want to talk to you about something.",
    "uid": "7626d26eccbd4148",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 517.91,
    "end": 522.91
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's like, I would be like, okay, look at this, look at this being, not in the mood.",
    "uid": "a0ad12e1b974b499",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 523.91,
    "end": 531.91
  },
  {
    "text": "And he said, I wanted to talk to you about the time that you said that I hurt your feelings.",
    "uid": "b1ce20fa6190539c",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 534.7,
    "end": 538.7
  },
  {
    "text": "The time that I hurt your feelings when I told you you should go to business school.",
    "uid": "f29ee8b1cc495eb6",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 538.7,
    "end": 548.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I said, oh, yeah.",
    "uid": "f80a354c432d0242",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 549.96,
    "end": 550.96
  },
  {
    "text": "That hurt my feelings, but what really hurt my feelings was telling me my career was the ways to my time and",
    "uid": "ac2cafb409298a74",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 551.96,
    "end": 558.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I wasted my intelligence.",
    "uid": "12865a2cdbb90657",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 559.96,
    "end": 560.96
  },
  {
    "text": "That was hurtful.",
    "uid": "b7755b7680b04408",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 561.96,
    "end": 562.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And he said, and he started to cry.",
    "uid": "a09a69c198ad248e",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 563.96,
    "end": 566.96
  },
  {
    "text": "The robot started to cry.",
    "uid": "0f04f451eb7494bf",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 567.96,
    "end": 569.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And he said, I was wrong.",
    "uid": "a26b971bf27c9378",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 569.96,
    "end": 572.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And I wanted to apologize for that.",
    "uid": "713fd0a0bd3635ad",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 573.96,
    "end": 575.96
  },
  {
    "text": "He said that I never understood you as a child.",
    "uid": "8a22a0534bc51bb9",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 576.96,
    "end": 580.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I didn't get you at all.",
    "uid": "4b9ea784a16ae669",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 581.96,
    "end": 582.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And I tried to project onto you my life and my route.",
    "uid": "a7bc6d69af8a354e",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 583.96,
    "end": 588.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And I expected you to take that exact same route.",
    "uid": "59bd0197e7a85f7a",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 589.96,
    "end": 592.96
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'm realizing that it's not the child's responsibility to teach the parent who they are.",
    "uid": "68e540163b62945f",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 593.96,
    "end": 606.1
  },
  {
    "text": "It's the parents responsibility to learn who the child is.",
    "uid": "ae7e5aef39caea29",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 607.1,
    "end": 611.1
  },
  {
    "text": "And I didn't do that.",
    "uid": "b0e4435e3e9c58e6",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 612.1,
    "end": 613.1
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'm sorry.",
    "uid": "ce28c67baf532f67",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 614.1,
    "end": 615.1
  },
  {
    "text": "And I said, so, and I'm crying too.",
    "uid": "532a2171b8a27482",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 618.34,
    "end": 622.34
  },
  {
    "text": "I said, are you saying that if I said I was going to quit comedy and go to business school, you wouldn't support that anymore?",
    "uid": "a9db69144c98e7ba",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 622.34,
    "end": 633.34
  },
  {
    "text": "And he said, absolutely not.",
    "uid": "44f2c2556a2cf647",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 634.34,
    "end": 639.41
  },
  {
    "text": "He said that is the only thing in the world that you should be doing.",
    "uid": "2ba11bbe50b6dbdf",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 640.41,
    "end": 643.41
  },
  {
    "text": "And I was like, oh my gosh, I didn't even realize that I needed that so desperately to hear that.",
    "uid": "776e57873f289e6a",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 644.41,
    "end": 650.41
  },
  {
    "text": "And the only thing that really bums me out is that my mother wasn't there to hear that.",
    "uid": "547e9c82e1c60907",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 650.41,
    "end": 655.41
  },
  {
    "text": "To hear him tell me that.",
    "uid": "9c91bfd331655c8e",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 656.41,
    "end": 658.41
  },
  {
    "text": "This Thanksgiving, I went to Texas.",
    "uid": "ac85354264d33e92",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 660.82,
    "end": 664.82
  },
  {
    "text": "And we actually spent it with Rick's side of the family.",
    "uid": "47f5a4f922020ca4",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 665.82,
    "end": 670.82
  },
  {
    "text": "And I needed to get away and just be by myself.",
    "uid": "feee3918cea5c32c",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 672.82,
    "end": 676.82
  },
  {
    "text": "And I decided to drive to my mother and Rick's house.",
    "uid": "22703f89592ae3e2",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 676.82,
    "end": 680.82
  },
  {
    "text": "And when I pulled up into the driveway, I just had a full on breakdown just sobbing in the driveway.",
    "uid": "2c2a9531b1a1d047",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 681.82,
    "end": 691.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Because I was like, oh my gosh, my mother is not in that house.",
    "uid": "60bafb2d74ec7da9",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 694.13,
    "end": 698.13
  },
  {
    "text": "And of course, I knew that, but it just really hit me in the driveway.",
    "uid": "f4f0c68d83a7f11a",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 699.13,
    "end": 703.13
  },
  {
    "text": "And then I walked inside and the house still smelled like her.",
    "uid": "c9905ba003556b70",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 703.13,
    "end": 708.13
  },
  {
    "text": "And everything was just so quiet. I was just looking around and still photos that were framed just seemed so still.",
    "uid": "a4b2d293668418d6",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 709.13,
    "end": 719.13
  },
  {
    "text": "Just moments in time caught and just gone forever.",
    "uid": "fe192e55dca3bde5",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 720.13,
    "end": 726.13
  },
  {
    "text": "And all the photos were still just placed where my mother had placed them over the years.",
    "uid": "6bcae674070671d6",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 727.13,
    "end": 732.57
  },
  {
    "text": "And I started opening drawers because I wanted to just see something of my mother.",
    "uid": "5749bcbc46cab632",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 732.57,
    "end": 740.97
  },
  {
    "text": "She would write little notes to herself like, you know, Dennis, 2pm, tomorrow.",
    "uid": "f1f7f8c8d54ac995",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 741.97,
    "end": 745.97
  },
  {
    "text": "And she was an artist.",
    "uid": "1e29e1ffae2892f5",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 746.97,
    "end": 748.97
  },
  {
    "text": "And she would sketch me perfectly on a napkin when I was just sitting around.",
    "uid": "ac98712f289ba8cb",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 749.97,
    "end": 753.97
  },
  {
    "text": "And so I was just looking for those kinds of things in the drawers.",
    "uid": "9d76f748ab9bf65e",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 754.97,
    "end": 757.97
  },
  {
    "text": "And there wasn't anything in there.",
    "uid": "a928c4f80321ea2d",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 758.97,
    "end": 759.97
  },
  {
    "text": "And I went to open a closet and there's nothing there.",
    "uid": "cc2e7f8a8587a2fb",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 759.97,
    "end": 764.97
  },
  {
    "text": "And I was finding nothing. And any drawers or closets. And I just started going around the house.",
    "uid": "516dabe71032a67a",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 767.57,
    "end": 772.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Just running around, just trying to find something.",
    "uid": "fdb8e09ec1c09ba3",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 773.57,
    "end": 775.57
  },
  {
    "text": "And then I was in this panic and just crying even harder.",
    "uid": "c8696e39df44eb3f",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 776.57,
    "end": 779.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Rick had gutted the house out.",
    "uid": "943b6799f781ae15",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 780.57,
    "end": 782.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Like he had when I was a child with a trash bag.",
    "uid": "997c6988830c4eda",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 783.57,
    "end": 787.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Everything was gone. And I was like, that is, I'm done with this person. I couldn't believe I had fallen for that conversation.",
    "uid": "a27a6d6da27860ae",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 787.57,
    "end": 794.57
  },
  {
    "text": "And I was so ready to write him off immediately of his done.",
    "uid": "261d4efddfd1d804",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 795.57,
    "end": 799.57
  },
  {
    "text": "And I called him on my cell phone. And he said, hello, Tig. How are you doing? I said, not good, not good.",
    "uid": "05b3026d1f133e2d",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 800.57,
    "end": 808.57
  },
  {
    "text": "All of my mother's things are on. And so were my childhood things.",
    "uid": "790386c89de632be",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 809.57,
    "end": 813.57
  },
  {
    "text": "And he said, oh, hold on a minute. Go into my bedroom.",
    "uid": "2274726002506b0d",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 813.57,
    "end": 817.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Go into my closet. And he started directing me.",
    "uid": "5d9aa4b57a626e7a",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 818.57,
    "end": 821.57
  },
  {
    "text": "And I was like, yeah. He said, look at the top shelf.",
    "uid": "9c6850b7992bb7be",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 822.57,
    "end": 825.57
  },
  {
    "text": "And up there, he had placed some of my mother's things.",
    "uid": "6f6b49809bf5189d",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 826.57,
    "end": 831.57
  },
  {
    "text": "And some of my childhood things. And, you know, I opened the box and there were, she was a dancer too.",
    "uid": "7113a25d610fb829",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 832.57,
    "end": 842.2
  },
  {
    "text": "There were her ballet slippers and photos. And I just was like, you're lucky.",
    "uid": "852a089219459c3c",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 842.2,
    "end": 850.2
  },
  {
    "text": "And although, you know, the four March when the word parents popped up on my collar ID, it represented my mother and Rick.",
    "uid": "d40e85dd81bf4ac4",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 851.2,
    "end": 875.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Now when the word parents pops up on my collar ID, it's only Rick.",
    "uid": "c455807204e06cb4",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 875.17,
    "end": 882.17
  },
  {
    "text": "We have very different cleanup techniques.",
    "uid": "409f9b4f9a1375ba",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 883.17,
    "end": 890.44
  },
  {
    "text": "But I'm learning to get used to that.",
    "uid": "973452fc9b3a7aac",
    "source": "The_Moth - The_Moth_Presents_Tig_Notaro_-_R2_Where_Are_You",
    "start": 891.44,
    "end": 895.82
  }
]